preference.name: PSM_global_effectivity_context
preference.preference_description: Specifies the default Effectivity Context used in the Structure Management application to configure the expression effectivity of Product Structure. The item_id of effectivity context should be specified and it is used for authoring effectivity options and specifying the effectivity conditions and criteria.
